sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:338:| Live deployment apply breaks the PAL router | Medium | High | PAL-029 through PAL-031 require deploy plan, backup primitive, and explicit apply approval. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:340:| PAL recommends Phase 2 too early | Medium | Medium | PAL-022 requires a report-only workflow with no Phase 2 execution action. |
sdp/prd-pal-2026-agentic-ops-platform.md:341:| Vast API connector causes spend or destructive actions | Low | High | PAL-036 and PAL-037 require stub-only Vast boundary and secret redaction tests. |
