sdp/prd-snapshot.md:109:- Restarting live PAL services.
sdp/prd-snapshot.md:125:PromptClaw remains the control plane. PAL router inference is treated as a reasoning service, not an executor.
sdp/prd-snapshot.md:127:### PAL Router
sdp/prd-snapshot.md:129:The remote PAL router remains a FastAPI service in front of Ollama. This PRD may add endpoints only when needed for safe operations, such as structured status or metrics. The existing `/health` and `/query` endpoints must remain backward compatible.
sdp/prd-snapshot.md:131:### PAL Knowledge Base
