sdp/prd-snapshot.md:200:| PAL-005 | Reject approvals for actions absent from the saved plan. | MUST | T1 | CLI returns nonzero and writes no execution artifact. |
sdp/prd-snapshot.md:201:| PAL-006 | Reject approvals for unknown action ids. | MUST | T1 | Test proves unknown ids never reach the action runner. |
sdp/prd-snapshot.md:202:| PAL-007 | Execute an approved saved action without a model call. | MUST | T1 | Fake PAL client records zero `query()` calls during replay. |
sdp/prd-snapshot.md:203:| PAL-008 | Write approval execution artifacts. | MUST | T1 | Artifact contains action id, status, timestamp, and redacted command output. |
