sdp/prd-snapshot.md:207:| PAL-012 | Add fake SSH runner support for PAL tests. | MUST | T1 | Tests run remote-action code without a real SSH connection. |
sdp/prd-snapshot.md:208:| PAL-013 | Create PAL source discovery function. | MUST | T2 | Test returns configured sample files. |
sdp/prd-snapshot.md:209:| PAL-014 | Add deterministic PAL knowledge chunking. | MUST | T2 | Test proves stable chunk ids for unchanged input files. |
sdp/prd-snapshot.md:210:| PAL-015 | Add PAL knowledge index writer. | MUST | T2 | `pal kb build` creates `.promptclaw/pal-kb/index.jsonl` or SQLite equivalent. |
sdp/prd-snapshot.md:211:| PAL-016 | Add PAL knowledge query command. | MUST | T2 | Query returns ranked snippets with source paths. |
sdp/prd-snapshot.md:212:| PAL-017 | Inject PAL knowledge into workflow prompts. | MUST | T2 | Prompt artifact includes a bounded `Knowledge Context` section. |
sdp/prd-snapshot.md:213:| PAL-018 | Add slow-inference context collection. | MUST | T2 | Workflow captures health, baseline token/s, GPU hints, and logs when available. |
sdp/prd-snapshot.md:214:| PAL-019 | Add slow-inference diagnosis CLI. | MUST | T2 | Command writes a diagnosis run artifact and performs no mutation. |
sdp/prd-snapshot.md:215:| PAL-020 | Add restart-validation workflow. | MUST | T2 | Command runs health, direct query, smoke, Tailscale, and process checks. |
sdp/prd-snapshot.md:216:| PAL-021 | Add shutdown-audit workflow. | MUST | T2 | Summary states shutdown enabled state, override state, and next shutdown window. |
sdp/prd-snapshot.md:217:| PAL-022 | Add Phase 2 readiness workflow. | MUST | T2 | Report scores each prerequisite and exposes no Phase 2 execution action. |
sdp/prd-snapshot.md:218:| PAL-023 | Standardize PAL workflow `run-summary.json`. | MUST | T1 | Every workflow writes required workflow/status/tool/action keys. |
sdp/prd-snapshot.md:219:| PAL-024 | Add PAL workflow artifact verifier. | MUST | T1 | Test fails a run missing required artifacts. |
sdp/prd-snapshot.md:220:| PAL-025 | Add PAL secret redaction verifier. | MUST | T1 | Test fails artifacts containing `PAL_SSH_KEY` or token-like values. |
sdp/prd-snapshot.md:221:| PAL-026 | Add PAL escalation artifact helper. | MUST | T1 | Missing SSH env and pending approval write `summary/escalation.md`. |
sdp/prd-snapshot.md:222:| PAL-027 | Create repo-managed PAL deployment manifest. | MUST | T2 | Manifest lists intended `/opt/pal` files and contains no secrets. |
sdp/prd-snapshot.md:223:| PAL-028 | Implement deploy diff model. | MUST | T2 | Fake remote test reports diff sets. |
sdp/prd-snapshot.md:224:| PAL-029 | Implement deploy-plan CLI. | MUST | T2 | Command prints plan with no remote writes. |
sdp/prd-snapshot.md:225:| PAL-030 | Implement deploy backup primitive. | SHOULD | T2 | Fake remote test stores changed files. |
sdp/prd-snapshot.md:226:| PAL-031 | Implement approved deploy-apply CLI. | SHOULD | T2 | Fake remote test requires approval flag. |
sdp/prd-snapshot.md:227:| PAL-032 | Implement rollback primitive. | SHOULD | T2 | Fake remote test restores backed-up files. |
