docs/discovery_20260329_095247.md:23:**Note:** There is also a remote server (CypherClaw, `ssh cypherclaw`) running Ubuntu 24.04, Dell 7090 SFF, i5-10505, 64GB RAM, no GPU yet (RTX A2000 12GB planned). That server runs the CypherClaw daemon, sdp-cli pipeline, and all agent execution. This discovery covers the **local MacBook** environment where PromptClaw source code lives.
